Invocation Name: cat fact
des:
Ask for Cat Facts, and learn about interesting things about cats that you may not know before!

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Cat Fact" or "Alexa, open Cat Fact to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
